    <item>
      <title>日本暗示中国海鲜禁令或将很快取得突破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府高级官员称，日本正与中国及国际原子能机构就福岛核电站附近海水检测进行谈判，这增加了北京方面可能放宽对日本海产品的禁令的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称犹太选民“与选举失败有很大关系”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/trump-vows-to-bring-back-travel-ban-bar-refugees-from-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在反犹太主义峰会上表示，如果他最终输掉总统大选，犹太选民应该为此负责，并抱怨自己在支持以色列后“没有得到公正的对待”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/trump-vows-to-bring-back-travel-ban-bar-refugees-from-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 00:44:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核电复兴让日本首相候选人团结起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本可能仍在努力应对福岛核灾难的深远影响，但争夺下一任领导人的政客们一致同意一件事：这个国家需要更多的核能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰铢升值 1998 年以来最大 泰国旅游业和出口面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/baht-s-biggest-rally-since-1998-threatens-thai-tourism-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国泰铢即将创下亚洲金融危机以来的最大季度涨幅，这可能会影响该国主要旅游业和出口业的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/baht-s-biggest-rally-since-1998-threatens-thai-tourism-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰总理预计随着经济复苏，公民外流将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-zealand-s-luxon-eyes-economic-rebound-after-tough-first-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森预计，随着利率下降和经济开始从长期低迷中复苏，离开新西兰的公民将会减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-zealand-s-luxon-eyes-economic-rebound-after-tough-first-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
